    {
      "id": "l5-foods",
      "type": "theory",
      "title": "Food and drink words",
      "body": "# Food and drink\n\nEveryday food and drink words:\n\n- **Water** (पानी) · **Tea** (चाय) · **Milk** (दूध)\n- **Bread** (रोटी) · **Rice** (चावल) · **Fruit** (फल)\n- **Vegetable** (सब्ज़ी) · **Apple** (सेब)\n\nMany of these are **uncountable** in English: we say *some water* (कुछ पानी), not *a water*. You count them with a container: *a glass of water* (एक गिलास पानी), *a cup of tea* (एक कप चाय)."
    },
